user.description:
Select the number entity that controls your heating curve offset.

{info}

Works with MyUplink (cloud), nibe_heatpump (local Modbus/NibeGW), or a template number wrapping modbus.write_register.

gespot.description:
Optionally configure spot price for 15-minute price optimization.

{detection_info}

**Recommended:** Use `current_price` sensor for real-time quarter-hour pricing.

optional_sensors.description:
Optional sensors and manual overrides. Leave a field empty to use automatic discovery.

{dm_note}

The override fields at the bottom are for setups where discovery cannot find your sensors (generic Modbus, renamed entities).
